metadata.name: National Professional Basketball League - 2025/26 Season
metadata.description: Professional track competition dataset featuring 20 teams, double round-robin format (380 fixtures), broadcast windows, revenue optimization, and national travel logistics. Difficulty: ⭐⭐⭐⭐
metadata.notes: This dataset tests schedulers on: broadcast window allocation, revenue maximization through optimal slot selection, strict competitive balance, long-distance travel optimization, and arena availability coordination.
